  "description": "Terracraft is a Fabric mod for Minecraft that adds content from Terraria in a way that doesn't feel out of place in vanilla.",
  "body": "<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/O9Eb5uB.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/O9Eb5uB.png\" width=\"1456\" height=\"380\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Requires <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Fabric API</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Version <span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">1.18.2</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">If you have any questions or suggestions, join the Discord!&nbsp;<a class=\"anchor-1MIwyf anchorUnderlineOnHover-2qPutX\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"https://discord.gg/SC8gz36NvT\" role=\"button\" href=\"https://discord.gg/SC8gz36NvT\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://discord.gg/SC8gz36NvT</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Terracraft is a Fabric mod for Minecraft that adds content from Terraria in a way that doesn't feel out of place in vanilla. Parity with Terraria is a bit lenient, but we plan to have all 5000+ features represented in some way.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/RZJ40t81Q_4\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 36px;\">Gallery</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mZRoHOS.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/mZRoHOS.png\" width=\"726\" height=\"400\" /></span><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PCqlKLT.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/PCqlKLT.png\" width=\"726\" height=\"400\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GklKV2H.png\" alt=\"https:/